[node name="Label2" type="Label" parent="." unique_id=662072057]
modulate = Color(0.28235295, 0.26666668, 0.2627451, 1)
offset_left = 15.0
offset_top = 65.0
offset_right = 105.0
offset_bottom = 95.0
text = "
art is not communication. make art without the
pretense that it will allow anything to become
more clearly understood by anyone except your-
self.

there is no way to really understand games, so
long as we stick to definitions of \"game\" that
are dependent on a \"player\", or on any \"play.\"

an unplayed game remains a game. an unexplored
maze remains a maze. an unsolved riddle, still
a riddle. still, still, still, still, still.

still the game eludes= comprehension. the book
is just what it is. what is a game?

a game describes a volume of space, a possible
arrangement and another, and another, and ano-
ther. a game is a collection of states. a game
is an argument, a pink argument. the argument,
the game, is pink, is a game, is a pink game.

there can not be a definition of \"game\" unless
it escapes the tyranny of the player. there is
no player in the game. the player resides out-
side, unreachable. the player argues pink, but
the game is only a pink argument. it's pink. a
game is a pink argument.

droqen"
label_settings = ExtResource("8_hv3is")
